{
  "stem": "22685.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- and this-- but this deal was going on for a while.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everything was-- until it went that the big powers made an agreement.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They moved the border from Graz to, I think, a different town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And now we have-- we had a problem with the British.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The British were stopping us all over the place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In the British zone, we already-- it was not a question of secrecy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we just couldn't cross the border.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to Budapest in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we created a Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We, we printed all kind of forms with stamps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we became a Red Cross, sending people for a-- from a British camp in Klagenfurt, which it was, to Albania-- Jews from the camps.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After a couple of months came a letter from the Albanian government.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It didn't have so many Jews before the war, how many we sent?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we started to send to Italy Jews-- everything to, to be able to go to Italy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And from there, it's already-- everything was organized in Italy, the-- all the organizations, they had camps, and the cooperation of the Italian government, and everything.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So God works in mysterious ways-- comes a delegation of the Greek Red Cross to visit their quote, 'nationals' in Klagenfurt and for a-- they say it Yiddish, [YIDDISH], for even-- for our medicine.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't have one Greek Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Nobody spoke Greek.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They talked-- we told them, tell a story, that you were born in Salonika.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Your parents went to Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You were born.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And after, your parents went when--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But of course, it-- and after a few weeks, we're getting a letter from the Austrian authorities that we should present ourselves.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
